            Story

Once upon a time, There lived a monkey who recites on a Berry tree which was on the bank of a river. In the same forest
there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day, the crocodile came to the bank of the river and took a rest under the tree. The kind-hearted monkey
offered him some fruits. Then the crocodile came back the next for the some more fruits as he loved them. As days passed by, the crocodile and monkey became good friends.
The monkey wanted to make a outfit for himself from the crocodile's skin. Then he slowly started to be his friend by feeding him the berries.
The berries were delicious and the crocodile liked it a lot. After sometime, the monkey started poisoning the berries. Monkey was very cruel
